fm: int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {         vector<int> pos(200, -1);         int start = 0, res = 0;         for (int i = 0; i < s.size(); ++i) {             if (pos[s[i]] != -1) {                 res = max(res, i - start);                 start = max(start, pos[s[i]] + 1);             }             pos[s[i]] = i;         }         res = max(res, static_cast<int>(s.size()) - start);         return res;     }

fm: int lengthOfLIS(vector<int> &nums) {         auto size = nums.size();         if (size == 0)             return 0;         vector<int> seq(1, nums[0]);         for (int i = 1; i < size; ++i) {             int mid = 0, x = 0, y = seq.size();             while (x < y) {                 mid = x + (y - x) / 2;                 if (seq[mid] < nums[i])                     x = mid + 1;                 else                     y = mid;             }             if (y == seq.size())                 seq.push_back(nums[i]);             else                 seq[y] = nums[i];         }         return seq.size();     }
